  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/34fbbd1d7084c6d37430d6d148d6bf23.avif?t=1738069233\" width=400 height=90 /></span><br>Immerse yourself in the world of <strong>Deadlocked</strong>, a cute little <strong>top-down shooter</strong> that pits you against waves of crafty robot foes— battle through unique environments, utilizing an arsenal of powerful weapons, adorable pet buddies and juicy character upgrades. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/cb8227411b1033a9072457f40e1ee051.poster.avif?t=1738069233\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/cb8227411b1033a9072457f40e1ee051.webm?t=1738069233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/cb8227411b1033a9072457f40e1ee051.mp4?t=1738069233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Strategically dodge, shoot, and obliterate enemies while uncovering the mysteries of Deadlocked. Unleash your skills in fast-paced combat, conquer challenging enemies, and defeat unique bosses. With fun visuals, responsive gameplay and multiple loadout possibilities, Deadlocked offers an electrifying experience for those seeking high-octane action.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/eb1226caff11b5d739e58bdfeffd3684.avif?t=1738069233\" width=401 height=95 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/b1a4d5cda1caa6e6e49d1d8c307e1188.poster.avif?t=1738069233\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/b1a4d5cda1caa6e6e49d1d8c307e1188.webm?t=1738069233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/b1a4d5cda1caa6e6e49d1d8c307e1188.mp4?t=1738069233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/c3928e77478f2d293d86125016397ab9.avif?t=1738069233\" width=401 height=95 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/4f8c4945a53c38d51c3dfe6bc7cd6d0e.poster.avif?t=1738069233\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/4f8c4945a53c38d51c3dfe6bc7cd6d0e.webm?t=1738069233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/4f8c4945a53c38d51c3dfe6bc7cd6d0e.mp4?t=1738069233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/0fe2a4c7240ae81349e79ed17a7dd908.avif?t=1738069233\" width=401 height=95 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/691c3826c573239f1c8af5b559d04da3.poster.avif?t=1738069233\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/691c3826c573239f1c8af5b559d04da3.webm?t=1738069233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2562100/extras/691c3826c573239f1c8af5b5